data, so zero/nonzero comparison remains unavailable until an explicit bridge is
supplied.
-/
structure FLZModCuspLabelThetaInsulatedCuspZeroLocalLabelObjectConstructionAudit
    (audit : endpoint.LogVolumeChartAudit)
    (l : PrimeGeFive) where
